# Parity item #3: the menu row carries a LIVE local count — "Download queue (1)" for the
# one queued line below (count_lines reads the pak's download-queue.txt, no network).
desc Download queue row shows the live count and reports the engine RESULT line verbatim
config paired
seeded
sdfile+ Tools/tg5040/Lodor.pak/download-queue.txt
pick 0|Download queue (1)
pick 2|
engine 0|RESULT downloaded=2 failed=0 remaining=0
expect_exit 0
expect_trace ENGINE --download-queue -> rc=0
expect_trace PRES timeout=3 msg='RESULT downloaded=2 failed=0 remaining=0'
